# Temple Eye tracking Madeline
placements.entities.templeEye.tooltips.followMadeline=(From max480's Helping Hand) Tick this checkbox to make the eye follow Madeline instead of Theo.

# Camera Catchup Speed Trigger
placements.triggers.MaxHelpingHand/CameraCatchupSpeedTrigger.tooltips.catchupSpeed=Raise this value to have the camera scroll quicker to its target. Vanilla values are 8 during the temple fall cutscene, and 1 everywhere else.

# Flag Touch Switch
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/FlagTouchSwitch.tooltips.flag=The session flag this touch switch sets. Give the same to multiple touch switches and switch gates to group them.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/FlagTouchSwitch.tooltips.icon=The name of the icon for the touch switch (relative to objects/MaxHelpingHand/flagTouchSwitch), or "vanilla" for the default one.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/FlagTouchSwitch.tooltips.persistent=If enabled, the touch switch will stay active when the player dies or changes rooms.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/FlagTouchSwitch.tooltips.inactiveColor=The switch colour when not triggered yet.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/FlagTouchSwitch.tooltips.activeColor=The switch colour when triggered, but the group is not complete yet.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/FlagTouchSwitch.tooltips.finishColor=The switch colour when the group is complete.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/FlagTouchSwitch.tooltips.smoke=Whether the touch switch emits smoke when the group is complete.

# Flag Switch Gate
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/FlagSwitchGate.tooltips.flag=The session flag this switch gate reacts to. Give the same to multiple touch switches and switch gates to group them.
