placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/FlagSwitchGate.tooltips.inactiveColor=The gate icon colour when not triggered yet.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/FlagSwitchGate.tooltips.activeColor=The gate icon colour when triggered, but the group is not complete yet.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/FlagSwitchGate.tooltips.finishColor=The gate icon colour when the group is complete.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/FlagSwitchGate.tooltips.sprite=The texture for the gate block.

# Customizable Crumble Platform
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/CustomizableCrumblePlatform.tooltips.texture=What texture to use for the crumble block.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/CustomizableCrumblePlatform.tooltips.oneUse=If checked, the platform will not respawn once it crumbled.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/CustomizableCrumblePlatform.tooltips.respawnDelay=The delay in seconds before the platform respawns after it crumbled (vanilla is 2 seconds).
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/CustomizableCrumblePlatform.tooltips.grouped=Whether this crumble platform should be "grouped" with crumble platforms that are next to it and also have the option enabled.\nAll crumble platforms in a "group" crumble together when the player steps on / grabs one of them.

# Upside Down Jump Thru
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/UpsideDownJumpThru.tooltips.texture=Changes the appearance of the platform. Should be in the same format as vanilla for static jumpthrus, and a 8x8 image for animated ones.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/UpsideDownJumpThru.tooltips.animationDelay=The delay in seconds between 2 frames of animation. Leave to 0 for no animation.

# Sideways Jump Thru
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/SidewaysJumpThru.tooltips.texture=Changes the appearance of the platform. Should be in the same format as vanilla for static jumpthrus, and a 8x8 image for animated ones.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/SidewaysJumpThru.tooltips.animationDelay=The delay in seconds between 2 frames of animation. Leave to 0 for no animation.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/SidewaysJumpThru.tooltips.left=Whether the solid side of the jumpthru is the left side.

# One-Way Invisible Barrier (Horizontal)
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/OneWayInvisibleBarrierHorizontal.tooltips.left=Whether the solid side of the barrier is the left side.

# Custom Summit Checkpoints
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/CustomSummitCheckpoint.tooltips.firstDigit=The first digit to display. (You can make your own by dropping textures in the Graphics/Atlases/Gameplay/MaxHelpingHand/summitcheckpoints/texturename folder.)
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/CustomSummitCheckpoint.tooltips.secondDigit=The second digit to display. (You can make your own by dropping textures in the Graphics/Atlases/Gameplay/MaxHelpingHand/summitcheckpoints/texturename folder.)

# Respawning Jellyfish
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/RespawningJellyfish.tooltips.bubble=Whether the entity should hover in the air before being grabbed.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/RespawningJellyfish.tooltips.tutorial=Whether the entity should show the usage tutorial.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/RespawningJellyfish.tooltips.respawnTime=The jellyfish will respawn at its starting location after this amount of time (in seconds) after being destroyed.

