placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/GroupedTriggerSpikesRight.tooltips.behindMoveBlocks=Determines whether the trigger spikes appear behind move blocks. Not supported for dust spikes.

# Rainbow Spinner Color Controller
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/RainbowSpinnerColorController.tooltips.colors=The colours the rainbow spinners in the room will take, separated by commas.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/RainbowSpinnerColorController.tooltips.gradientSize=The distance required to achieve a complete loop across all colours.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/RainbowSpinnerColorController.tooltips.loopColors=Determines how the colors loop. For example, if 3 colours A, B and C are specified:\n- when unchecked, the colours will cycle in the following order: A > B > C > B > A\n- when checked, the colours will cycle in the following order: A > B > C > A > B > C
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/RainbowSpinnerColorController.tooltips.persistent=If checked, the chosen colors will persist until the player enters a room with another Rainbow Spinner Color Controller.\nIf unchecked, the chosen colors will only apply to the current room.

# Strawberry Collection Field
placements.triggers.MaxHelpingHand/StrawberryCollectionField.tooltips.delayBetweenBerries=Whether there should be a 0.3 second delay between each berry collection (like when berries are collected on the ground).
placements.triggers.MaxHelpingHand/StrawberryCollectionField.tooltips.includeGoldens=Whether this trigger should collect golden strawberries and other berries that block normal collection.

# Customizable Refill
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/CustomizableRefill.tooltips.twoDash=Whether the refill should give two dashes.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/CustomizableRefill.tooltips.oneUse=Whether the refill should respawn after being used.
placements.entities.MaxHelpingHand/CustomizableRefill.tooltips.respawnTime=The delay (in seconds) before the refill respawns after being collected.
